## Common Development Tasks

### Adding a New Project
1. Add project image to `public/projects/photos/`
2. Edit `src/pages/Projects.tsx`
3. Add to `projects` array with proper interface
4. Include: title, description, tags, imageUrl, githubUrl, liveUrl

### Adding Photos
1. Optimize image (<500KB, JPEG format)
2. Add to `public/photos/[category]/`
3. Update `src/data/photoManifest.ts`
4. Follow naming convention: `location-description-number.jpg`

### Updating Experience
1. Edit `src/pages/Experience.tsx`
2. Update `experiences` array
3. Include: company, role, period, description, technologies

### Modifying Analytics
1. Service logic: `src/services/analytics.ts`
2. Dashboard UI: `src/pages/Analytics.tsx`
3. Auth component: `src/components/AdminAuth.tsx`
4. Hook: `src/hooks/useAnalytics.ts`

