## Troubleshooting
- **404 on page refresh**: Check `public/404.html` script
- **Analytics not working**: Verify `.env` Firebase config
- **Images not loading**: Check public folder paths (no `/public` in URL)
- **Build fails**: Check TypeScript errors, verify dependencies
- **Dark mode not persisting**: Check localStorage implementation
- **Routing issues**: Verify basename in React Router (should be `/`)

